 >How To Play</h2><br>Drone move - W, A, S, D and Mouse movement.<br>Turn On / Off drone - Z<br>Record Canvas On / Off (At the heliport ) -  O<br>Object interact - F and Mouse left click<br><br>More about system you can find in the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy SimulDrone</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892500/extras/c789d301d3bb2f404622f103e3090542.avif?t=1703116051\" width=682 height=384 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892500/extras/c0aaeb8e09d0e7f7eafc0dc6eba48cda.avif?t=1703116051\" width=682 height=384 /></span>",
